  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/251d8c1200d14a25e3f7d8280e3537fc.apng?t=1770069172\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/251d8c1200d14a25e3f7d8280e3537fc.poster.avif?t=1770069172\" class=\"bb_img\" width=374 height=56 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into epic battles! Choose the perfect combinations of different types of weapons and upgrade your ship throughout the adventure, creating unique combinations that will help you survive! Harness your skills to destroy hordes of alien ships and giant bosses, using strategy and a powerful arsenal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/fe51924e8a89d5d71f29285088a26e45.poster.avif?t=1770069172\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/fe51924e8a89d5d71f29285088a26e45.webm?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/fe51924e8a89d5d71f29285088a26e45.mp4?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GUNFIELD</strong> is perfect for fans of <strong>Vampire Survivors</strong> and lovers of vertical scrolling shooters like <strong>Tyrian</strong>. Combine your combat skills and tactical thinking to achieve victory in every battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/1c5c30feced249cee5642432f63bcf52.poster.avif?t=1770069172\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/1c5c30feced249cee5642432f63bcf52.webm?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/1c5c30feced249cee5642432f63bcf52.mp4?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/5acad26b613085a8d702aad40f6f5d11.poster.avif?t=1770069172\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/5acad26b613085a8d702aad40f6f5d11.webm?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/5acad26b613085a8d702aad40f6f5d11.mp4?t=1770069172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What awaits you:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse builds:</strong> Create unique combinations of weapons and abilities in each run to become the true hero of the galaxy!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic battles:</strong> Challenge entire alien armies and fight colossal bosses in dynamic, thrilling combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arsenal upgrades:</strong> Unlock and improve powerful weapons and abilities to become an unbeatable fighter!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Variety of ships and pilots:</strong> Discover new ships, each with unique traits that influence your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exciting levels:</strong> Explore beautiful pixelated locations, uncovering new worlds and amazing adventures at every turn!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls:</strong> Play using mouse, keyboard, joystick, or touchscreen – choose your preferred way and join the battle!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The time has come! Are you ready for the fight?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/bb6498c831bec9e973e827412b9c86f1.avif?t=1770069172\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p>",
