Controls:</strong> Play using mouse, keyboard, joystick, or touchscreen – choose your preferred way and join the battle!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The time has come! Are you ready for the fight?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2305900/extras/bb6498c831bec9e973e827412b9c86f1.avif?t=1770069172\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p>",
